the mill on the floss is a 1936 british drama film directed by tim whelan and starring frank lawton , victoria hopper , geraldine fitzgerald and james mason .   it was based on the novel the mill on the floss by george eliot .   it was made at shepperton studios .   although he is not credited in the film the producer basil dean , who was married to the leading lady victoria hopper , was heavily involved in the planning and the production of the film .